    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You are adept at using shadows to conceal your attacks.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Int 13, Blind-Fight, Combat Expertise, Bluff 3 ranks, darkvision or low-light vision racial trait.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>While you have concealment from an opponent, you gain a +2 bonus on attack and damage rolls against that opponent.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When you have total concealment from an opponent, you can spend 2 stamina points to increase your bonuses on attack and damage rolls from this feat to +4.",
